data.description: SOLAR PAYOFF WITH FULL-PRICE OFFER! Adorable, move-in ready house nestled in the vibrant heart of Phoenix. This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts a large patio and private yard, north/south exposure, and a large kitchen with ample storage. Added bonus of solar panels and no HOA. In this highly convenient location you'll find shopping, groceries, healthcare facilities, entertainment options, and the Lookout Mountain trailhead all within a mile's reach. All appliances convey with the home. Recent updates include fresh interior and exterior paint, new sinks/fixtures in the bathrooms, and new grass and modern irrigation. ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AVAILABLE at low fixed rate of 2.625% (details available through listing agent). This would also make a GREAT RENTAL INVESTMENT - no HOA & central location
